deep_space.ponder.void_engine.text_1: Build your Void Engine on a ship.
deep_space.ponder.void_engine.text_2:
Build a 3x3 cube from Engine Frames and Engine Viewports.
Place a Void Core in the middle.
deep_space.ponder.void_engine.text_3: Add a Void Engine Interface. The Void Core will wake up.
deep_space.ponder.void_engine.text_4: With the Void Engine complete, you can fast-travel through the Wormhole dimension.
deep_space.ponder.void_engine.text_5: To do this, supply the interface with a supply of FE, and a redstone signal.
